values: Have not written in a while... No one said this life would be easy.

Today was pimp, I woke up smoked!!Score, wake and bake. LOL. I've been sitting here listening to reggae and writing music all day. I explored the universe, contemplated life, visited my self, and enjoyed it. I cant wait to get some Salvia Divinorum. Piece, Love, and Happiness.

I'm still floating from last night. Some good shit. So I was sitting here stoned and I forgot my hand was hurt so I popped my knuckles and it cracked really loudly and I looked at my knuckle and it was fine, so I guess it was just dislocated so bad that it displaced my knuckle. And you know what I'm gonna go smoke again.;-)
Today sucked. Got stood up again! For the 4th time by the 3rd girl. Blah, fuck it, Im'a go get stoned and go to the doc for my hand.

Man today was terrible but all i needed to do was smoke a big splif and relax. As in the words of the great Bob Marley "Don't worry about a thing, cause every little thing gonna be alright". Good night world. Good night Jah.

Well today was an interesting day. Woke up, worked school, weed, some more school, some more weed, and then my dogs got into a fight. I get them outside, still fighting, spray em with the hose, still fighting, try to rip them apart, can't, so i start punching them in the head, still fucking fighting, i finally get them apart. One runs away, the other one gets out my hand and chases it. About this time my neighbor jumps over the fence and kicks the aggressor in the chest. This makes the dog lose its grip, the dog runs away. We get them separated by a fence. It's about this time a notice my knuckle is destroyed, i mean fucked up. Looks like jello pudding that was placed under my skin in place of my knuckle too close to my pinkie, just sagging there.
